Category,Technology Used,Purpose in Your Project
Frontend UI,Streamlit,"Rapid web application development, handling chat interface, sidebar controls, and state management."
Orchestration,LangChain,"Managing the logic flow, chaining prompts, handling retrievers, and connecting LLMs to tools."
LLM Provider,Groq,Ultra-fast inference API. Used for Llama 3.1 (Chat/RAG) and Gemma 2 (Web Search/Correction).
Embeddings,HuggingFace,all-MiniLM-L6-v2. Converts text into vector representations for semantic search.
Vector Database,FAISS (CPU),Stores document embeddings for fast similarity search (Dense Retrieval).
Retrieval Algorithms,BM25 & Ensemble,BM25 for keyword search. EnsembleRetriever combines FAISS + BM25 for hybrid search accuracy.
Reranking,Cross-Encoder,ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2. Re-scores retrieved documents based on deep semantic relevance.
Web Search,Tavily API,Optimized search engine for AI agents to fetch real-time data from the web.
Safety & Guardrails,Microsoft Presidio,Detects and handles PII (Personally Identifiable Information).
Safety & Guardrails,Detoxify,"Detects toxic, biased, or harmful language in user inputs."
Audio/Vision,Whisper & Llama Vision,Whisper (via Groq) for speech-to-text; Llama Vision (via Groq) for image analysis.
